Package org.husky.emed.ch.models.entry

Class EmedEntryDigest

java.lang.Object
org.husky.emed.ch.models.entry.EmedEntryDigest
Direct Known Subclasses:
EmedDisEntryDigest, EmedMtpEntryDigest, EmedPadvEntryDigest, EmedPreEntryDigest
public abstract class EmedEntryDigest extends Object
Represents the digest of an EMED document item entry. This class is declined in subclasses EmedMtpEntryDigest, EmedPreEntryDigest, EmedDisEntryDigest and EmedPadvEntryDigest.
Author:
Quentin Ligier
